Subject: Re: [T2] VW van, how to tighten side view mirrors?

On Sun, 11 Jan 2004 ARoman4047(-at-)aol.com wrote:

> I've used caulk to set the mirror,
> but I'm open to a better suggestion...

Waterproof double sticky tape to hold the glass in place, then hot melt
glue to fill the gap between the glass and the metal.  Leave a small gap
at the bottom of the mirror to allow moisture to vent.

George
